Wellness Wednesday 💫 here a few things I think are great to keep healthy and well when traveling
Got my vitamin iv at @thesolutioniv to boost immunity before getting on the plane ✈️ 
Stopped in for a sweat sesh at @perspiresaunastudio to detox and relieve sore muscles
Made some green juice to get all those yummy whole foods!
What do you like to do to keep well?
#wellness #saunatherapy #infaredsauna #greensmoothies #vitaminivtherapy

Had my very first float session at @floatclinic last night.
Check out my stories (also saved in hilights) to see my experience. You are basically floating in a sensory deprivation tank pitch black light proof and sound proof in epsom salt infused water. There’s a shower right outside the door for before and after your float along with earplugs. I definitely worked through a fear of the dark I didn’t realize was intense as it was. After I was calmer I got to enjoy the experience as time went on and I relaxed. Will you try a float session?
#floating #sensorydeprivation #wellness #relaxation #growth

A lovely visit to the @oseamalibu spa for a Cranial Wave facial. So lovely and so relaxing!
I’ve been a long time user of the brand - but needed a refresh and my esthetician gave me some products to add to my routine . Basically she said I was pretty dry and dehydrated. Products listed below!
Ocean cleansing milk🤍 soothing gentle cleanse 
Hyaluronic sea serum🤍 adding after my vitamin c serum for daytime keeps the skin hydrated and plump
Ocean Eyes 🤍 for the delicate eye area; smooths fine lines and instantly refreshes
Advanced moisture cream 🤍 I can’t live without this moisturizing cream. The BEST
#makeup #makeupartist #skin #skincare #facials #wellness #osea #oseamalibu #losangelesmakeupartist
